      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and is entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, with the leather upholstery still firm and smelling fresh, and all electronic components functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. A buyer can expect a car that looks and drives like it's brand new.",
