      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly start? This vehicle is ready for a new lease on life! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great foundation for anyone handy with tools or looking for a parts car. It's a diamond in the very rough, priced to sell for someone who sees the potential!",
